dct_alternative_sm: Regnum Salomonicum seu tabula digesta ad libros judicum, regnum, paral. et prophetarum per Eparchias, XII, mox regna duo
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, islands off coast, settlements, territorial boundaries of the twelve tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
Features an illustration of a compass rose and a decorative cartouche.
